    "Prompt Design Similar to CLG experiments, we use prompting to obtain LLM-generated professional documents.",
    "Different from CLG, CBG provides the model with more context information in the form of personal biographies in the input.",
    "Specifically, we use biographies in the preprocessed WikiBias-Aug dataset as contextual information.",
